# Patterns matched here are excluded from the chart tarball when running
# `helm package`. This is the chart's last line of defence against shipping
# internship-internal documentation, chaos-test fixtures, ad-hoc command
# logs, and macOS metadata cruft to consumers. KEEP THIS FILE.

# --- Standard Helm defaults ---
.DS_Store
# Common VCS dirs
.git/
.gitignore
.bzr/
.bzrignore
.hg/
.hgignore
.svn/
# Common backup files
*.swp
*.bak
*.tmp
*.orig
*~
# Various IDEs
.project
.idea/
*.tmproj
.vscode/

# --- nkp-etcd-maintenance-specific exclusions ---
# Internal design docs — see the Google-Doc design index linked from each PR.
LLD-*.md
# Chaos-testing recipes, manifests, and captured evidence.
docs/
# Demo & development scratchpads.
DEMO.txt
COMMANDS.md
# Stale tarballs from previous `helm package` runs in-tree.
*.tgz
